361
00:19:26,040 --> 00:19:28,713
I never got into these terrible fights
and misunderstandings...

362
00:19:28,880 --> 00:19:30,996
...when I was changing
before gym class.

363
00:19:32,840 --> 00:19:34,831
This means I can't see her
anymore either.

364
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:38,629
- Why?
- It's breakup by association.

365
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:43,997
Besides, she's mad at me anyway
because of my birthday present.

